Interface Message

All Known Implementing Classes:
MessageImpl
public interface Message

This interface includes methods common to FillMessage and CancelMessage. The methods correspond to gets and sets of data members.

Author:
Urvi

Nested Class Summary

          Describes the type of message, valid values are Cancel and Fill.
